01/11/2002
TIRANA, Albania -- Minister of Local Governance and Decentralisation Ben Blushi met Thursday (31 October) with US Ambassador James Jeffrey to discuss reforms aimed at decentralising the infrastructure.
Blushi thanked Washington for specific programmes of the USAID and the Urban Institute, saying such regional strategies and consolidation of local administrations will improve the quality of public services.
(ATA - 31/10/02)
